{"tid":375973,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"講真呢次4:2事件，可以睇到人其實好撚蠢。","createTime":"2017-08-26T18:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T21:42:10.000Z","uid":44035,"like":115,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe65f46e2682c4220f339456e24df9335fc47f2","tid":375973,"uid":44035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:19:37.000Z","msg":"我唔知有幾多個係假膠，但我肯定真係有人會信條傻鳩，大注或者直頭訓身落去...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老實講，我開頭見到佢中爆冷3:2波膽，都有一刻覺得佢好勁，甚至有懷疑過真係有內幕料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但係佢如果係咁撚勁啊，洗撚同你班傻仔分享咩，益班三唔識七既人有咩著數啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日行一善咩真係？好心咁大個人咪咁戇鳩啦好冇啊，佢唔中佢拍下羅友就走左去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一啲損失都冇<br />\n<br />\n係，中29倍波膽係好勁，咁易發達，佢做緊李嘉誠啦，洗係個論壇同你班傻仔鳩up咩？成班戇鳩真係以為賺錢好易，冇撚腦，抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲平時自以爲聰明過人，高人一等既連登仔，其實都係好撚柒蠢，平時就識笑鳩人，到真係發生係自己身上，咪又係成堆羊群心理。連少少獨立思考能力都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難怪要控制香港人咁容易。<br />\n<br />\n最後講多句，好心蠢撚到咁就快撚啲死左佢咪撚係度獻世好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"9e4422e3c681c007564849b8b13b8ca937616805","tid":375973,"uid":44035,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:25:20.000Z","msg":"見到咩用左grant loan錢黎賭，買左幾皮野果啲 唉。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時真係忍唔住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa9fd3f0854eb49c1b09148f2f90a35a00dd584","tid":375973,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e425c4ca3f6ae21a9f53feee66466134a7a2216","tid":375973,"uid":32753,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:30:29.000Z","msg":"馬後砲<br />\n不過真"},{"pid":"91da0c6590ad15b454efc40e4124aa1b53575527","tid":375973,"uid":44035,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬後砲<br />\n不過真</blockquote><br />\n我認我係，如果佢中埋呢次，我下次會跟埋都唔定。<br />\n我唔係要話自己有幾醒，只係發覺原來人真係好蠢。"},{"pid":"11c5c41db521b82374824d1ac7b06d660c95bbab","tid":375973,"uid":19556,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:37:14.000Z","msg":"40倍變15倍即係好撚多傻鳩跟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e02bb748efe9003a132a171e139c00a6dffe9bc","tid":375973,"uid":105879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:37:32.000Z","msg":"知自己冇咩運,決定一生唔賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c39f34a6dafa48ad40699d4c384783bccfb809","tid":375973,"uid":44035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>知自己冇咩運,決定一生唔賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賭返黎既錢，來得快去得快，留唔住的"},{"pid":"21f7c1bf7af8bd574bcfb951205bcdfa9c14c320","tid":375973,"uid":21255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T18:38:36.000Z","msg":"40倍打撚到賽前17倍就知有幾多弱智"},{"pid":"1bd1c5a96657617727d1a7cfed0afd764f079fa1","tid":375973,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re